metadata.name: Honorary Doge #1
metadata.description:
Honorary Membership was given to people who earned the respect of the Doge Art Club.

Honorary members made a direct or indirect impact on the project. Some of them made sure the world knows about DAC, some earned the respect during special community events, and some were just extraordinary people Genesis Doges looked up to.

Honorary Doges are not part of the Doge Art Club collection, and have no member privileges.
